column_description: A unique identifier for each meeting
The identifier of the client associated with the meeting, linking to the `Clients` table
The result or outcome of the meeting, such as 'Report', 'Summary', or 'Vote results'
The type of meeting, such as 'Team', 'Group', or 'Company'
A flag indicating whether the meeting is billable (1) or not (0)
The date and time when the meeting started
The date and time when the meeting ended
A brief description of the purpose of the meeting, such as 'get proposal done' or 'weekly report'
value_description: get proposal done, vote for solutions, weekly report, monthly report

column_description: Additional details or notes about the meeting, such as 'absent staff' or other relevant information
